('AN0001989', 'WC0001989', 'ADV0039', '2025-10-02 12:32:01.097', 'VIDEO_CONFERENCE', '63', 'Client, Spouse, Advisor', 'Follow-up on previous discussion about charitable giving strategy. Client wishes to donate $11989 to alma mater. Reviewed options including direct gift, donor-advised fund, and qualified charitable distribution from IRA. Recommended QCD given clients age (72) and RMD requirements. Will coordinate with charity for proper documentation.', 'Charitable giving strategy; recommending QCD for $11989 donation', '1) Coordinate QCD with charity. 2) Obtain tax documentation. 3) Confirm receipt of funds.', '2026-04-11', 'ESG Investing, Values Alignment, Portfolio Transition', 'POSITIVE', '2026-02-17 14:32:01.097'),
