('AN0001991', 'WC0001991', 'ADV0041', '2025-10-02 09:12:01.097', 'EMAIL_FOLLOW_UP', '77', 'Client, Advisor, Tax Specialist', 'Quarterly check-in call. Markets have been volatile but client portfolio has held up well due to diversification. Client mentioned potential job change that could impact cash flow needs. Discussed contingency plans including reducing contributions temporarily if needed. Reviewed progress on retirement goal - currently at 72% of target with 8 years to go. On track assuming 7% average returns.', 'Quarterly check-in; potential job change discussed; retirement goal on track at 72%', '1) Monitor employment situation. 2) Prepare contingency cash flow scenarios. 3) Next quarterly call in October.', '2026-04-17', 'Retirement Planning, Income Strategy, Social Security', 'POSITIVE', '2026-02-17 14:32:01.097'),
