('AN0002069', 'WC0000069', 'ADV0019', '2025-09-26 23:12:01.097', 'EMAIL_FOLLOW_UP', '23', 'Client, Spouse, Advisor', 'Follow-up on previous discussion about charitable giving strategy. Client wishes to donate $12069 to alma mater. Reviewed options including direct gift, donor-advised fund, and qualified charitable distribution from IRA. Recommended QCD given clients age (72) and RMD requirements. Will coordinate with charity for proper documentation.', 'Charitable giving strategy; recommending QCD for $12069 donation', '1) Coordinate QCD with charity. 2) Obtain tax documentation. 3) Confirm receipt of funds.', '2026-04-23', 'ESG Investing, Values Alignment, Portfolio Transition', 'POSITIVE', '2026-02-17 14:32:01.097'),
('AN0002070', 'WC0000070', 'ADV0020', '2025-09-26 21:32:01.097', 'ANNUAL_REVIEW', '30', 'Client, Advisor, Portfolio Manager', 'Conducted comprehensive annual portfolio review with client. Reviewed performance versus benchmarks - portfolio outperformed by 1.2% YTD. Discussed asset allocation and confirmed it remains aligned with stated risk tolerance. Client expressed satisfaction with current strategy but inquired about increasing international exposure. Recommended gradual shift of 5% from domestic to international equities over next quarter. Also discussed estate planning updates needed following birth of grandchild.', 'Annual review complete; increasing intl exposure 5%; estate planning update needed', '1) Implement 5% shift to international. 2) Contact estate attorney for document updates. 3) Schedule follow-up in 90 days.', '2026-04-26', 'Tax Optimization, Roth Conversion, Loss Harvesting', 'VERY_POSITIVE', '2026-02-17 14:32:01.097'),
