('AN0002809', 'WC0000809', 'ADV0009', '2025-08-06 13:52:01.097', 'QUARTERLY_CHECK_IN', '28', 'Client, Spouse, Advisor', 'Follow-up on previous discussion about charitable giving strategy. Client wishes to donate $12809 to alma mater. Reviewed options including direct gift, donor-advised fund, and qualified charitable distribution from IRA. Recommended QCD given clients age (72) and RMD requirements. Will coordinate with charity for proper documentation.', 'Charitable giving strategy; recommending QCD for $12809 donation', '1) Coordinate QCD with charity. 2) Obtain tax documentation. 3) Confirm receipt of funds.', '2026-05-09', 'Goal Progress, Cash Flow, Market Update', 'POSITIVE', '2026-02-17 14:32:01.097'),
('AN0002810', 'WC0000810', 'ADV0010', '2025-08-06 12:12:01.097', 'PHONE_CALL', '35', 'Client, Advisor, Portfolio Manager', 'Conducted comprehensive annual portfolio review with client. Reviewed performance versus benchmarks - portfolio outperformed by 1.2% YTD. Discussed asset allocation and confirmed it remains aligned with stated risk tolerance. Client expressed satisfaction with current strategy but inquired about increasing international exposure. Recommended gradual shift of 5% from domestic to international equities over next quarter. Also discussed estate planning updates needed following birth of grandchild.', 'Annual review complete; increasing intl exposure 5%; estate planning update needed', '1) Implement 5% shift to international. 2) Contact estate attorney for document updates. 3) Schedule follow-up in 90 days.', '2026-05-12', 'Market Volatility, Risk Tolerance, Long-term Strategy', 'VERY_POSITIVE', '2026-02-17 14:32:01.097'),
('AN0002811', 'WC0000811', 'ADV0011', '2025-08-06 10:32:01.097', 'VIDEO_CONFERENCE', '42', 'Client, Advisor, Tax Specialist', 'Quarterly check-in call. Markets have been volatile but client portfolio has held up well due to diversification. Client mentioned potential job change that could impact cash flow needs. Discussed contingency plans including reducing contributions temporarily if needed. Reviewed progress on retirement goal - currently at 72% of target with 8 years to go. On track assuming 7% average returns.', 'Quarterly check-in; potential job change discussed; retirement goal on track at 72%', '1) Monitor employment situation. 2) Prepare contingency cash flow scenarios. 3) Next quarterly call in October.', '2026-05-15', 'Liquidity Needs, Tax Planning, Withdrawal Strategy', 'POSITIVE', '2026-02-17 14:32:01.097'),
